            "Section conclusion: the CER authoring workflow is required to show the regulatory basis in Summary, explicit clinical benefits in Scope, a clear equivalence route, market/PMS/vigilance closure, SOTA-to-4.7 comparison, GSPR-linked manufacturer evidence analysis and section-level conclusions. Any missing item becomes a controlled patch, evidence request, human hold or DeerFlow rerun decision.",
